    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream! This beauty is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014it\u2019s like it just rolled off the lot yesterday. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, you won't find a single scratch or speck of dust. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for that perfect, 'as-new' feel without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
