    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This investment-grade E46 M3 features the high-revving S54B32 power unit, complete with individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double VANOS system. The chassis has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and the rod bearings have been proactively addressed, ensuring structural and internal longevity. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. The factory finish remains in showroom state, while the suspension geometry maintains its original crispness, offering unparalleled feedback through the hydraulically assisted steering rack. A mechanically flawless example for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
