    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved by a single dedicated owner. The exterior features the original factory paint, which retains a deep, mirror-like luster protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. The body is laser-straight with absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' condition; the premium leather upholstery shows zero bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and the interior still retains its original new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the heated seat elements, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships, and I possess a comprehensive folder of all maintenance records. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is free of any corrosion or fluid seepage. It currently sits on pristine alloy wheels wrapped in a fresh set of high-performance tires with less than 500 miles on them. This sale includes both original keys, the factory window sticker, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom-fit indoor car cover. For the enthusiast who demands a flawless example, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class.",
